name: Farm Equipment Set - 8 Piece
description: This 8 piece set comes complete with two tractors.  A farm tractor and a big 8 wheel articulating tractor.  It also comes with a corn picker/combined, hay wagon with 6 bales, cultivator, planter, manure spreader and a grain wagon.  With this set your young farmer with be ready to work in the fields.  Made of solid wood and finished with mineral oil for a non-toxic and child safe product.  These items can be purchased individually at http://toysbyjohn.blogspot.com.  See my blog for dimensions along with more toys like my Barn set which coordinate with the Farm set.

name: Kitchen Dining Set
description:
This set of furniture and appliances is a great gift for your little one.  Fits great in most doll houses and with Barbie.  The refridgerator and freezer opens and closes as the oven does too.  You get the choice of a square table with four legs or the oval one with a pedestal.  The set comes complete with one table, four chairs, refridgerator, and stove.  Made of solid wood and finished with a non-toxic, child safe mineral oil.  Order today to give that special child a long time of enjoyment.

More doll furniture is available at http://toysbyjohn.blogspot.com

Square Table Dimensions-
8 inches long by 5-1/2 inches wide by 4 inches high

Round Table Dimensions-
8 inches long by 5 inches wide by 4 inches high

Refridgerator Dimensions-
9 inches high by 4 inches wide by 2-3/4 inches deep

Stove/Oven Dimensions-
5 inches high by 4 inches wide by 2-3/4 inches deep
